# 📌 Project Showcase Website

A simple project showcase webpage displaying various projects with a clean UI and smooth GSAP animations on scroll. The website is built using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and GSAP** for animations.

---

## ✨ Features

✅ Responsive project cards layout  
✅ Hover effects for better UI/UX  
✅ Smooth **GSAP ScrollTrigger** animation  
✅ Easy-to-modify project list  
✅ Minimalist and clean design

---

## 🚀 Demo

🔗 Live Website: (https://mtabba.github.io/MarathonProject/)

---

## 📂 Folder Structure

```
📁 project-showcase
│── 📂 assets            # Images & icons used in the project
│── 📄 index.html        # Main HTML file
│── 📄 stylesdark.css    # CSS for styling
│── 📄 styleslight.css   # CSS for styling
│── 📄 script.js         # JavaScript (GSAP animations)
│── 📄 README.md         # Project documentation
```

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- **HTML5** – Structure of the website
- **CSS3** – Styling & responsiveness
- **JavaScript (GSAP)** – Smooth scroll animations

---

## 📥 Installation & Usage

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/mtabba/MarathoProject.git
   ```
2. **Navigate to the project folder**
   ```sh
   cd MarathonProject
   ```
3. **Open `index.html` in your browser**

